431
00:42:18,199 --> 00:42:20,199
[SPEAKER_02] Samo ti Oliver.

432
00:42:20,199 --> 00:42:24,199
[SPEAKER_02] Tvoj dođek i ispraćaj velikog Olivera.

433
00:42:25,199 --> 00:42:26,199
[SPEAKER_02] I tad si rekao...

434
00:42:26,199 --> 00:42:28,199
[SPEAKER_02] Tad si rekao...

435
00:42:28,199 --> 00:42:35,199
[SPEAKER_02] Da se nisi rodio u Splitu, da bi bio od ovce, je li tako?

436
00:42:35,199 --> 00:42:42,199
[SPEAKER_02] Je li tako misliš? Je li misliš da to dakle si determinira i koliko ćeš napraviti?

437
00:42:42,199 --> 00:42:49,199
