458
00:46:06,280 --> 00:46:08,039
[SPEAKER_02] Ne, da bi on rekao, jeli.

459
00:46:08,039 --> 00:46:10,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ha, dobro, mislim, ali to je Split.

460
00:46:10,579 --> 00:46:11,280
[SPEAKER_01] To je Split.

461
00:46:11,280 --> 00:46:11,780
[SPEAKER_01] To je Split.

462
00:46:11,780 --> 00:46:18,320
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, ne možeš se ti ljuti na te stvari, i to je jednostavno tako, ja sam se okrenio, ja otišao.

463
00:46:18,320 --> 00:46:25,800
