486
00:48:41,739 --> 00:48:44,760
[SPEAKER_02] Kako se oteš na reći nešto za ovo?

487
00:48:44,780 --> 00:48:47,719
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja sam ga, mislim, prvo kad sam izabran, to je,

488
00:48:47,719 --> 00:48:50,400
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, nema veće časti.

489
00:48:50,400 --> 00:48:51,400
[SPEAKER_01] Je to vrh.

490
00:48:51,400 --> 00:48:52,400
[SPEAKER_01] To je vrh.

491
00:48:52,400 --> 00:49:00,980
[SPEAKER_01] To je ono, stavili su me u muzej, to je ono, živ sam, ali kad sam nošao u taj Hall of Fame muzej u Njuport,

492
00:49:00,980 --> 00:49:06,400
