01:05:56,059 --> 01:05:57,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to su bili trenizi

755
01:05:57,800 --> 01:06:00,679
[SPEAKER_01] gdje te izbaci iz avuta

756
01:06:00,679 --> 01:06:01,460
[SPEAKER_01] i kažu ti te,

757
01:06:01,460 --> 01:06:04,039
[SPEAKER_01] ajde, će mi mene doli ispri škole,

758
01:06:04,039 --> 01:06:05,699
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam koja je ono doli škole.

759
01:06:05,699 --> 01:06:09,559
[SPEAKER_01] Pa uzbrdo, pa imaš videlicu,

760
01:06:09,559 --> 01:06:11,380
[SPEAKER_01] pa ona ravnica gdje je zroškoj ori,

761
01:06:11,380 --> 01:06:13,099
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda onih tri stoji nešto skala.

762
01:06:13,099 --> 01:06:14,099
[SPEAKER_01] To je bila krug.

763
01:06:14,099 --> 01:06:18,420
[SPEAKER_02] To je gospodo sve Marijan da ne znači,

764
01:06:18,420 --> 01:06:19,159
[SPEAKER_02] ali mi pričamo.

765
01:06:19,159 --> 01:06:20,380
[SPEAKER_01] I to je to.

766
01:06:20,380 --> 01:06:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] I bilo je,

767
01:06:22,159 --> 01:06:23,480
[SPEAKER_01] toliko imaš vrimena,

768
01:06:23,480 --> 01:06:24,900
[SPEAKER_01] došla si gore,

769
01:06:24,900 --> 01:06:26,280
[SPEAKER_01] ideš odmah doli

770
01:06:26,280 --> 01:06:27,340
[SPEAKER_01] i ideš ponovo.

771
01:06:27,340 --> 01:06:29,559
[SPEAKER_01] I nije bilo ono,

772
01:06:29,559 --> 01:06:30,719
[SPEAKER_01] umoran sam.

773
01:06:30,719 --> 01:06:34,400
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan par puta sam rekao,

774
01:06:34,400 --> 01:06:35,380
[SPEAKER_01] povraća mi se.

775
01:06:35,380 --> 01:06:37,480
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, ajde,

776
01:06:37,480 --> 01:06:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] tu sa strane povrati

777
01:06:38,960 --> 01:06:39,880
[SPEAKER_01] i ajde, ide.

778
01:06:39,880 --> 01:06:40,739
[SPEAKER_02] I nastaj.

779
01:06:40,739 --> 01:06:41,559
[SPEAKER_01] A sad,

780
01:06:41,559 --> 01:06:42,760
[SPEAKER_01] kad je ono,

781
01:06:42,760 --> 01:06:43,480
[SPEAKER_01] ajme,

782
01:06:43,480 --> 01:06:44,320
[SPEAKER_01] povraća,

783
01:06:44,320 --> 01:06:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] samo i odmah

784
01:06:45,880 --> 01:06:47,599
[SPEAKER_01] sidi voda,

785
01:06:47,599 --> 01:06:48,940
[SPEAKER_01] energeska pića.

786
01:06:48,940 --> 01:06:50,079
[SPEAKER_01] Kako je energeska pića?

787
01:06:50,079 --> 01:06:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, treniralo se,

788
01:06:52,539 --> 01:06:54,679
[SPEAKER_01] trčali su se dionice,

789
01:06:54,679 --> 01:06:55,980
[SPEAKER_01] trčalo se po Marijanu,

790
01:06:56,280 --> 01:06:57,119
[SPEAKER_01] ima sam puno,

791
01:06:57,119 --> 01:06:58,820
[SPEAKER_01] ono, dođeš na vrata,

792
01:06:58,820 --> 01:06:59,380
[SPEAKER_01] na Marijan,

793
01:06:59,380 --> 01:07:00,820
[SPEAKER_01] sretnjaš neko vamo

794
01:07:00,820 --> 01:07:02,840
[SPEAKER_01] do instituta i nazad,

795
01:07:02,840 --> 01:07:05,139
[SPEAKER_01] pa idemo gori,

796
01:07:05,139 --> 01:07:06,559
[SPEAKER_01] po trim stazi.

797
01:07:06,559 --> 01:07:06,960
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

798
01:07:06,960 --> 01:07:09,019
[SPEAKER_01] nisam uopće razmišljao,

799
01:07:09,019 --> 01:07:10,059
[SPEAKER_01] oću li krivo stat?

800
01:07:10,059 --> 01:07:11,199
[SPEAKER_01] Oću li ja,

801
01:07:11,199 --> 01:07:12,659
[SPEAKER_01] ono je neravno,

802
01:07:12,659 --> 01:07:13,219
[SPEAKER_01] oću li ja,

803
01:07:13,219 --> 01:07:14,679
[SPEAKER_01] izvrni nogu.

804
01:07:14,679 --> 01:07:16,559
[SPEAKER_01] Moglo se desiti.

805
01:07:16,559 --> 01:07:18,800
[SPEAKER_01] Meni nikad u životu palo nije na pamet.

806
01:07:18,800 --> 01:07:19,480
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, a gore,

807
01:07:19,480 --> 01:07:21,059
[SPEAKER_02] lud, ovakav, onakav.

808
01:07:21,059 --> 01:07:22,880
[SPEAKER_02] A jel ti to usadio?

809
01:07:22,880 --> 01:07:24,139
[SPEAKER_02] Na početku,

810
01:07:24,139 --> 01:07:25,320
[SPEAKER_02] kad smo dole bili,

811
01:07:25,940 --> 01:07:26,619
[SPEAKER_02] si pričao,

812
01:07:26,619 --> 01:07:28,780
[SPEAKER_02] da bi ti otac znao,

813
01:07:28,780 --> 01:07:30,360
[SPEAKER_02] kad ste mali bili na firule,

814
01:07:30,360 --> 01:07:31,460
[SPEAKER_02] a živili ste

815
01:07:31,460 --> 01:07:33,099
[SPEAKER_02] u kineski zid,

816
01:07:33,099 --> 01:07:33,559
[SPEAKER_02] je li tako,

817
01:07:33,559 --> 01:07:34,940
[SPEAKER_02] da kad ne bi bio

818
01:07:34,940 --> 01:07:36,059
[SPEAKER_02] zadovoljan sa treningom,

819
01:07:36,059 --> 01:07:36,900
[SPEAKER_02] da bi ti rekao,

820
01:07:36,900 --> 01:07:37,639
[SPEAKER_02] ja idem na auton,

821
01:07:37,639 --> 01:07:38,360
[SPEAKER_02] ti ideš pješke,

822
01:07:38,360 --> 01:07:40,739
[SPEAKER_02] ali dođi prije mene doma.

823
01:07:40,739 --> 01:07:40,980
[SPEAKER_01] Je,

824
01:07:40,980 --> 01:07:42,599
[SPEAKER_01] ali nekad nije bio zadovoljan

825
01:07:42,599 --> 01:07:43,159
[SPEAKER_01] s treningom,

826
01:07:43,159 --> 01:07:44,280
[SPEAKER_01] nego kad sam baš ono

827
01:07:44,280 --> 01:07:47,099
[SPEAKER_01] pretjera sa svojim divljanjem,

828
01:07:47,099 --> 01:07:48,980
[SPEAKER_01] i ludilo on,

829
01:07:48,980 --> 01:07:49,500
[SPEAKER_01] i onda,

830
01:07:49,500 --> 01:07:50,780
[SPEAKER_01] više nije znao,

831
01:07:50,780 --> 01:07:51,239
[SPEAKER_01] i bilo je,

832
01:07:51,239 --> 01:07:51,559
[SPEAKER_01] ajde,

833
01:07:51,559 --> 01:07:54,099
[SPEAKER_01] idem aš doši doma prije mene,

834
01:07:54,099 --> 01:07:55,260
[SPEAKER_01] on bi krenio auton,

835
01:07:55,260 --> 01:07:56,179
[SPEAKER_01] a onda,

836
01:07:56,179 --> 01:07:58,119
[SPEAKER_01] kroz rivu,

837
01:07:58,119 --> 01:07:58,800
[SPEAKER_01] trčat,

838
01:07:58,800 --> 01:08:00,280
[SPEAKER_01] pa ko bi to prije,

839
01:08:00,360 --> 01:08:00,940
[SPEAKER_01] ono doba,

840
01:08:00,940 --> 01:08:02,119
[SPEAKER_01] da te neko vidi,

841
01:08:02,119 --> 01:08:03,079
[SPEAKER_01] da brže hodaš,

842
01:08:03,079 --> 01:08:04,840
[SPEAKER_01] bi te ovdje ovoga radikula.

843
01:08:04,840 --> 01:08:06,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam to,

844
01:08:06,539 --> 01:08:07,260
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

845
01:08:07,260 --> 01:08:09,719
[SPEAKER_01] Marmontovi su išli aut,

846
01:08:09,719 --> 01:08:10,800
[SPEAKER_01] kroz rivu su išli,

847
01:08:10,800 --> 01:08:11,920
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam šprinta,

848
01:08:11,920 --> 01:08:15,780
[SPEAKER_01] nisam znao,

849
01:08:15,780 --> 01:08:18,140
[SPEAKER_01] to je bilo šprintanje,

850
01:08:18,140 --> 01:08:19,520
