851
01:08:19,520 --> 01:08:22,039
[SPEAKER_01] tako da,

852
01:08:22,039 --> 01:08:25,060
[SPEAKER_01] mora sam doći prije njega.

853
01:08:25,060 --> 01:08:26,680
[SPEAKER_01] Mora si doći.

854
01:08:26,680 --> 01:08:27,939
[SPEAKER_02] Ope, ono što se vraćaš,

855
01:08:27,939 --> 01:08:29,039
[SPEAKER_02] nijema druge opcije,

856
01:08:29,039 --> 01:08:30,079
[SPEAKER_02] ne posuoji druga opcija.

857
01:08:30,279 --> 01:08:30,819
[SPEAKER_01] ne postoji,

858
01:08:30,819 --> 01:08:32,319
[SPEAKER_01] ali samo ja nisam zna,

859
01:08:32,319 --> 01:08:33,220
[SPEAKER_01] je li on,

860
01:08:33,220 --> 01:08:34,819
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam vidio da on krenija,

861
01:08:34,819 --> 01:08:37,619
[SPEAKER_01] da li se on vratija,

862
01:08:37,619 --> 01:08:39,079
[SPEAKER_01] ili on stvarno iša dom.

863
01:08:39,079 --> 01:08:40,020
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da, da, da.

864
01:08:40,020 --> 01:08:41,380
[SPEAKER_01] To nije bilo meni,

865
01:08:41,380 --> 01:08:42,100
[SPEAKER_01] uopće ne razmije,

866
01:08:42,100 --> 01:08:43,319
[SPEAKER_01] ovdje ne gleda,

867
01:08:43,319 --> 01:08:44,300
[SPEAKER_01] ne ideš u taj rizik.

868
01:08:44,300 --> 01:08:46,680
[SPEAKER_01] I ja trčim,

869
01:08:46,680 --> 01:08:48,220
[SPEAKER_01] ja trčim,

870
01:08:48,220 --> 01:08:50,720
