871
01:08:50,720 --> 01:08:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] Zovu Mašu,

872
01:08:53,119 --> 01:08:55,060
[SPEAKER_01] nemoj sad prijatelju,

873
01:08:55,060 --> 01:08:56,920
[SPEAKER_01] majko, bradraga.

874
01:08:56,920 --> 01:08:58,100
[SPEAKER_02] To su strašne.

875
01:08:58,100 --> 01:08:58,880
[SPEAKER_02] A reci mi,

876
01:09:00,199 --> 01:09:02,140
