880
01:09:07,159 --> 01:09:07,460
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

881
01:09:08,579 --> 01:09:10,359
[SPEAKER_02] Koje trenere pamtiš ovako?

882
01:09:10,359 --> 01:09:15,479
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, pametim sve ove trenere,

883
01:09:15,479 --> 01:09:16,039
[SPEAKER_01] što se nima,

884
01:09:16,039 --> 01:09:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] Šeolaci stari,

885
01:09:17,079 --> 01:09:18,060
[SPEAKER_01] koji mi naučija.

886
01:09:18,060 --> 01:09:19,520
[SPEAKER_01] Kaćer, da.

887
01:09:19,760 --> 01:09:20,260
[SPEAKER_01] kaćer.

888
01:09:20,260 --> 01:09:21,220
[SPEAKER_01] Pa,

889
01:09:21,220 --> 01:09:23,239
[SPEAKER_01] pokojni Zoran Ilić,

890
01:09:23,239 --> 01:09:25,279
[SPEAKER_01] pa bila je

891
01:09:25,279 --> 01:09:26,359
[SPEAKER_01] teta Vera,

892
01:09:26,359 --> 01:09:29,439
[SPEAKER_01] mora si to prvo da odeš na turnire.

893
01:09:29,439 --> 01:09:31,479
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je bila onda,

894
01:09:31,479 --> 01:09:33,779
[SPEAKER_01] kome trenira.

895
01:09:33,779 --> 01:09:34,460
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim,

896
01:09:34,460 --> 01:09:35,800
