898
01:09:39,279 --> 01:09:41,899
[SPEAKER_01] on je bio kao otac.

899
01:09:41,899 --> 01:09:43,340
[SPEAKER_01] On je govori da si mu sin,

900
01:09:43,340 --> 01:09:44,199
[SPEAKER_01] da si mu kao sin.

901
01:09:44,279 --> 01:09:45,279
[SPEAKER_01] i on je naučija

902
01:09:45,279 --> 01:09:47,119
[SPEAKER_01] ne samo stvari

903
01:09:47,119 --> 01:09:48,760
