907
01:09:52,680 --> 01:09:54,020
[SPEAKER_01] svaki turnir,

908
01:09:54,020 --> 01:09:54,819
[SPEAKER_01] ostavi ovome,

909
01:09:54,819 --> 01:09:55,439
[SPEAKER_01] masero,

910
01:09:55,439 --> 01:09:56,380
[SPEAKER_01] nešto ti špana,

911
01:09:56,380 --> 01:09:57,600
