912
01:09:57,600 --> 01:09:58,479
[SPEAKER_01] daj mu nešto.

913
01:09:58,479 --> 01:10:00,760
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ti ljudi

914
01:10:00,760 --> 01:10:01,899
