915
01:10:01,899 --> 01:10:02,979
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno je on,

916
01:10:02,979 --> 01:10:06,060
[SPEAKER_01] imali smo mi ne suglasica,

917
01:10:06,060 --> 01:10:08,279
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja sam bio odličan za treniranje.

918
01:10:08,279 --> 01:10:09,859
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam mogo trenirati po cijelaj dan.

919
01:10:09,859 --> 01:10:11,460
[SPEAKER_01] I trčati, i igrati.

920
01:10:13,039 --> 01:10:15,100
