921
01:10:15,100 --> 01:10:16,640
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ja bi volio

922
01:10:16,640 --> 01:10:19,140
[SPEAKER_01] trenirati sad onoga Gorana.

923
01:10:19,140 --> 01:10:19,619
[SPEAKER_02] Nije li?

924
01:10:19,619 --> 01:10:21,600
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim da bi onda Goran

925
01:10:21,600 --> 01:10:23,680
[SPEAKER_01] bio čak i bolji igrač.

926
01:10:23,680 --> 01:10:26,600
[SPEAKER_01] Jer uz ovo iskustvo,

927
01:10:26,600 --> 01:10:27,760
[SPEAKER_01] što ja znam kod trener,

928
01:10:27,760 --> 01:10:29,800
[SPEAKER_01] da mu prenese neke stvari,

929
01:10:29,800 --> 01:10:31,020
[SPEAKER_01] da ga malo...

930
01:10:31,020 --> 01:10:32,060
[SPEAKER_02] A što bi promijenio,

931
01:10:32,060 --> 01:10:34,140
[SPEAKER_02] odnosno primijenio na njega?

932
01:10:34,140 --> 01:10:35,779
[SPEAKER_01] Pa primijenio bi prvo

933
01:10:35,779 --> 01:10:38,779
[SPEAKER_01] na meću neke stvari,

934
01:10:38,779 --> 01:10:41,380
[SPEAKER_01] da se malo drugačije ponaša,

935
01:10:41,380 --> 01:10:42,380
[SPEAKER_01] da bude malo...

936
