938
01:10:46,340 --> 01:10:49,520
[SPEAKER_01] Na nekim stvarima bi možda više radila.

939
01:10:49,520 --> 01:10:51,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, servis, ali opet,

940
01:10:51,079 --> 01:10:53,500
[SPEAKER_01] nije se sve vrtilo oko servisa.

941
01:10:53,500 --> 01:10:55,180
[SPEAKER_01] Osvoja sam na turnire i na zemlji.

942
01:10:55,180 --> 01:10:55,439
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno.

943
01:10:55,439 --> 01:10:58,399
[SPEAKER_01] E možda bi malo drugačije trenirao.

944
