947
01:11:01,939 --> 01:11:02,619
[SPEAKER_01] ne smiješ utege.

948
01:11:02,760 --> 01:11:02,960
[SPEAKER_01] i dalje.

949
01:11:02,960 --> 01:11:06,100
[SPEAKER_01] I ja znam,

950
01:11:06,100 --> 01:11:07,680
[SPEAKER_01] kad smo ja i Boško se sakrijevali,

951
01:11:07,680 --> 01:11:08,340
[SPEAKER_01] kad bi ja radila,

952
01:11:08,340 --> 01:11:09,760
[SPEAKER_01] da ne bi došao moj stari,

953
01:11:09,760 --> 01:11:11,359
