956
01:11:13,520 --> 01:11:15,060
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, to je bilo tada.

957
01:11:15,060 --> 01:11:17,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ali jednostavno,

958
01:11:17,260 --> 01:11:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] ta neka...

959
