962
01:11:23,500 --> 01:11:25,520
[SPEAKER_01] Kako ću ja biti trener nekom?

963
01:11:25,939 --> 01:11:27,500
[SPEAKER_01] A ja sam najsmireni trener na svijetu.

964
01:11:27,500 --> 01:11:30,760
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ta mirnoća,

965
01:11:30,760 --> 01:11:35,539
[SPEAKER_01] jer možda Bob Brett je ono,

966
01:11:35,539 --> 01:11:37,239
[SPEAKER_01] on je onaj stari kov,

967
01:11:37,239 --> 01:11:39,039
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je ili kako on kaže,

968
01:11:39,039 --> 01:11:39,659
[SPEAKER_01] ili nikako.

969
01:11:39,659 --> 01:11:41,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pa smo koji put imali,

970
01:11:41,960 --> 01:11:44,399
